name: Hami
dialog: Hi, P_name. What did you eat today?

name: 주인공
dialog: I haven't eaten yet. I'm about to eat now.

name: Hami
dialog: Then let's eat together. I just picked some vegetables from my garden. What should we make with these?

name: 주인공
dialog: There are spinach, lettuce, eggplant, and zucchini. How about bibimbap?

name: Hami
dialog: Sounds perfect! Bibimbap is the best-known dish in the world with perfect nutrition.

name: 주인공
dialog: Wow, bibimbap is so nutritious? How is it good for us?

name: Hami
dialog: Listen up carefully. Carbohydrates in rice provide energy for our activities.

name: Hami
dialog: Proteins in meat or eggs form various organs such as muscles, bones, skin, and blood vessels.

name: Hami
dialog: Foods high in protein include chicken breast, beef tenderloin, peanuts, tofu, and salmon.

name: Hami
dialog: Remember, eat a lot of high-protein foods to become strong!

name: Hami
dialog: Fat in sesame oil provides us with energy and maintains body temperature.

name: Hami
dialog: These three nutrients are essential for our bodies, so we need to eat them evenly.

name: 주인공
dialog: I want to eat bibimbap quickly! My mouth is watering.

name: Hami
dialog: My stomach is sending a signal that it wants to eat too.
비고: 비빔밥 완성전, 완성 후 2컷! (페이드 인,아웃 하면서 이미지 바꾸기)

name: Hami
dialog: Mmm, that was delicious! It tasted even better because we ate together, right?

name: 주인공
dialog: Yeah, it tasted good, was nutritious, and made us stronger.

name: 주인공
dialog: Hamiya! Next time, I'll prepare the food.

name: Hami
dialog: Oh, I'm looking forward to it! Remember the essential nutrients when preparing food!

name: end
